      <title>中国史上最多战机飞越台海要塞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/china-sends-most-warplanes-ever-across-key-line-with-taiwan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国派出创纪录数量的战机越过台湾海峡美国划定的边界 — — 而此时，台湾新总统正考虑出访美国，其中可能包括访问美国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/china-sends-most-warplanes-ever-across-key-line-with-taiwan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 03:10:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利总统奥尔班将在北约峰会后前往佛罗里达会见特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/hungary-s-orban-will-visit-trump-in-florida-after-nato-summit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，前总统唐纳德·特朗普将于周四在佛罗里达州会见匈牙利总理维克托·欧尔班，不到一周之前，他还在莫斯科会见了俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/hungary-s-orban-will-visit-trump-in-florida-after-nato-summit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 02:54:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将在比特币活动上发表讲话，以表达对加密货币的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/trump-to-address-bitcoin-btc-event-in-show-of-support-for-crypto</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据活动组织者称，唐纳德·特朗普将于本月晚些时候在一个比特币会议上发表讲话，此次讲话将凸显他对加密货币行业日益增长的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/trump-to-address-bitcoin-btc-event-in-show-of-support-for-crypto</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 00:42:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登首次与史塔默会晤欢迎英欧建立更紧密关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/biden-welcomes-closer-uk-europe-ties-in-first-starmer-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登称英国是连接北约联盟的“纽带”，并称赞新任首相基尔·斯塔默为建立与欧洲的更紧密关系所做的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/biden-welcomes-closer-uk-europe-ties-in-first-starmer-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 00:04:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国高达 300 亿英镑的预算缺口可能威胁里夫斯的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/uk-budget-hole-of-up-to-30-billion-may-threaten-reeves-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯面临高达 300 亿英镑（390 亿美元）的预算缺口，这将阻碍英国新政府修复该国陷入困境的公共服务的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/uk-budget-hole-of-up-to-30-billion-may-threaten-reeves-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平如何在六大会议上做出惊人举动，震惊世界</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/how-xi-can-shock-the-world-with-big-bang-moves-at-china-plenum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国有能力在一次高风险的政策会议上结束房地产危机，包括采取“一揽子解决方案”，即像美联储那样注入资金。但它不太可能立即采取行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/how-xi-can-shock-the-world-with-big-bang-moves-at-china-plenum</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议院民主党人呼吁更换候选人，拜登面临越来越大的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/schumer-open-to-replacing-biden-as-nominee-axios-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，一位参议院民主党人和越来越多的众议院议员一起呼吁总统乔·拜登下台，但他在党内面临越来越强烈的反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/schumer-open-to-replacing-biden-as-nominee-axios-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 22:13:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大计划购买潜艇，距离北约防御目标更近一步</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/canada-plans-to-buy-submarines-inching-closer-to-nato-defense-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多试图平息盟友的批评，该国表示将开始购买潜艇舰队，此举可能会增加其国防开支，以满足北约的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/canada-plans-to-buy-submarines-inching-closer-to-nato-defense-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 20:36:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥卡西奥·科尔特斯提议弹劾托马斯和阿利托法官，理由是他们收受了礼物</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/rep-alexandria-ocasio-cortez-moves-to-impeach-thomas-alito</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国众议员亚历山大·奥卡西奥·科尔特斯对最高法院法官克拉伦斯·托马斯和塞缪尔·阿利托提出弹劾条款，她称他们未能报告礼物并且拒绝回避与他们有利益冲突的案件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/rep-alexandria-ocasio-cortez-moves-to-impeach-thomas-alito</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 18:03:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北约批评中国在乌克兰问题上支持俄罗斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/nato-set-to-call-out-china-over-support-for-russia-s-war-machine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在有迹象表明北京正在为与乌克兰的冲突开发攻击无人机之际，北约领导人发表了北约史上最强硬的措辞，要求中国向俄罗斯提供军事支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/nato-set-to-call-out-china-over-support-for-russia-s-war-machine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:44:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
